00:03:11.020 --> 00:03:12.839
It wasn't that, there wasn't a need,

00:03:12.839 --> 00:03:15.399
it wasn't a fact that there were no one,

00:03:15.399 --> 00:03:17.460
no individuals there that needed healing,

00:03:17.460 --> 00:03:19.500
no, it wasn't that,

00:03:19.500 --> 00:03:22.139
