00:04:15.300 --> 00:04:17.980
what causes you, what causes me,

00:04:17.980 --> 00:04:21.679
what causes us to doubt, to not believe God.

00:04:21.679 --> 00:04:24.660
It's not because he's failed, amen,

00:04:24.660 --> 00:04:28.140
