00:04:31.579 --> 00:04:34.320
And so what is it that causes us to doubt?

00:04:34.320 --> 00:04:35.859
We noticed as we've studied

00:04:35.859 --> 00:04:37.459
through the portion of scripture,

00:04:37.459 --> 00:04:39.779
it's when the people got their eyes,

00:04:39.779 --> 00:04:43.299
those 10 bad spies as we refer to them,

00:04:43.299 --> 00:04:44.299
