00:05:23.579 --> 00:05:26.140
We've said that doubt and unbelief,

00:05:26.140 --> 00:05:28.940
it's sin and it must be dealt with

00:05:28.940 --> 00:05:30.540
and we understand that as we look

00:05:30.540 --> 00:05:31.880
