00:38:32.299 --> 00:38:35.339
and it can rattle us and get our attention

00:38:35.339 --> 00:38:38.179
but we have to say, no, no, I'm gonna get my eyes on Jesus,

00:38:38.179 --> 00:38:41.380
I'm gonna make that decision, I'm going to make the choice

00:38:41.380 --> 00:38:46.380
and exercise my will to trust God, to trust him

00:38:48.260 --> 00:38:51.820
because God wants his people to believe him.

00:38:53.080 --> 00:38:58.080
At times, if you're honest, doubt creeps up in our lives.

00:39:00.739 --> 00:39:02.339
How's this gonna work out?

00:39:02.339 --> 00:39:03.979
How are we ever going to?

00:39:03.979 --> 00:39:06.979
I wasn't preparing for, I didn't see this coming

00:39:09.219 --> 00:39:10.779
and doubt can start to creep in

00:39:11.979 --> 00:39:16.459
and if doubt creeps in, doubt wants to take over.

00:39:18.959 --> 00:39:22.700
Those weeds in the garden, they're not content

00:39:22.700 --> 00:39:26.059
just having a little corner of the garden bed, am I right?

00:39:27.059 --> 00:39:29.739
They want the whole thing, right?

00:39:33.299 --> 00:39:37.219
Doubt wants to consume, take over.

00:39:39.140 --> 00:39:39.979
Why?

00:39:39.979 --> 00:39:43.580
Because faith pleases God, faith is what caused us

00:39:43.580 --> 00:39:48.580
to step out, say I believe God, I wanna see God do something

00:39:49.580 --> 00:39:51.619
because God is able, let's pray.

00:39:51.619 --> 00:39:54.299
Father, we love you, thank you for loving us,

00:39:54.299 --> 00:39:55.779
thank you for the privilege of being able

00:39:56.500 --> 00:39:57.700
to study your word tonight.

00:39:58.559 --> 00:39:59.859
I pray, Father, that you.

00:39:59.859 --> 00:40:05.479
It would help us to conquer doubt in our lives.

00:40:05.479 --> 00:40:08.739
Oh, it won't be a one and done.

00:40:08.739 --> 00:40:12.079
We can conquer doubt today and something can happen tomorrow or next week

00:40:12.079 --> 00:40:18.079
that will cause that doubt to creep in and we have to go through the process.

00:40:18.079 --> 00:40:23.079
Lord, help us to stay in Your Word, to have our faith continuing to increase.

00:40:23.079 --> 00:40:27.779
Help us, Lord, to believe You, to live by faith.

00:40:27.779 --> 00:40:29.319
I pray that You'd bless our time of prayer.

00:40:29.319 --> 00:40:33.439
Thank You again for the privilege, the opportunity to enter into Your presence.

00:40:33.439 --> 00:40:34.439
You're a wonderful God.

00:40:34.439 --> 00:40:35.839
You do great things.

00:40:35.839 --> 00:40:37.559
Thank You that You hear us.

00:40:37.559 --> 00:40:45.679
What a blessing to think that we can pray, God of the universe, and that You hear us,

00:40:45.679 --> 00:40:50.879
that You're interested, that You answer us.

00:40:50.879 --> 00:40:54.279
God, I pray that You'd bless and we'll thank You for it.

00:40:54.279 --> 00:40:57.239
In Christ's name we pray, amen.

